  <summary date="2022-02-02T22:35:49Z" status="Introduced in House">Flag Code Modernization Act of 2021

This bill revises provisions regarding customs and practices with respect to the American flag.

Among other changes, the bill permits U.S. postal workers to wear the flag on their uniforms and modifies provisions regarding the position and manner of display of the flag.</summary>
